                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7457" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1174</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2186 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">问渠哪得清如许，为有源头活水来——LH公司内部转移定价的优化之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The river is always keeping clean, since there is inflowing water from its source —— The optimization of LH company&#39;s internal transfer pricing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李瑞,杨丰旭,谭飞 ,吴小越,姚鸿译</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">LH公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型国有炼化企业；内部转移定价；业财融合</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Large state-owned refining and chemical enterprises; Internal transfer pricing; Integration of industry and finance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">我国炼化行业过去凭借着粗放式管理大力刺激生产顺应时代需求，然而随着经济和技术的不断发展，我国炼化产品的供给和需求发生了巨大的变化，如今需要精细化管理、聚焦企业效益来应对百舸争流的经济全球化。本案例以大型国有炼化企业LH公司为例，讲述了该企业在时代变革下通过建立基于业财融合的内部转移定价体系实现涅槃重生的历程。LH公司深陷增收不增利的经营困境后，一改往日“以销定产”的管理思想和老旧的管理方法，通过作业成本法和业财一体化信息平台实现业财融合，在此基础上使用内部转移定价工具，充分发挥内部转移定价工具的市场压力传导作用，引导LH企业上至管理层下至基层员工有效进行降本增效，最终实现LH企业的涅槃重生。本案例旨在帮助学生理解内部转移定价工具以及该工具与业财融合的关系，同时希望能够为其他深陷困境的国有炼化企业提供一定参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the past, Chinese refining and chemical industry greatly stimulated production by extensive management. However, with the continuous development of economy and technology, the supply and demand of Chinese refining and chemical products have undergone great changes. Now it is necessary to respond to the economic globalization by refining management and focusing on enterprise benefits. This case takes LH Company, a large state-owned refining and chemical enterprise, as an example, and tells the process of the enterprise&#39;s nirvana and rebirth through the establishment of internal transfer pricing system based on the integration of industry and finance under the change of The Times. LH company was stuck in the business dilemma of increasing revenue but not increasing profit. Instead of the old management idea of &quot;selling to target production&quot; and the old management method, the integration of industry and finance is realized through activity-based costing and industry-finance integrated information platform. On this basis, it used the internal transfer pricing tool to give full play to the market pressure transmission effect of the internal transfer pricing tool. Guide LH employees from the management level down to the grassroots level to effectively reduce costs and increase efficiency, and finally realize the rebirth of LH enterprise. The purpose of this case is to help students understand the internal transfer pricing tool and the relationship between this tool and the integration of industry and finance. At the same time, it hopes to provide some reference for other state-owned refining and chemical enterprises in deep trouble.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部转移定价；业财融合；作业成本法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
